These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
City: liverpool, rome, miami, berlin, venice, san-francisco, colone
There are 7 different nationalities: american, brazilian, french, german, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
 2. the person traveling to berlin is not the russian##6
 3. the american is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 4. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
 6. the american is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere between the person traveling to rome and the brazilian##7
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the spanish##1
 9. the german is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the french##7
10. the french is on the left or right of the american##3
11. the mexican is on the far left##1
12. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
13. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
14. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
15. the person traveling to venice is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| City          | miami    | liverpool    | rome | san-francisco | berlin | venice    | colone |
| Nationality   | mexican | american | french  | russian   | german    | brazilian | spanish |

