The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, country, d&b, hip-hop, jazz, metal
 1. the fan of metal is between the person who likes green and the fan of country##2
 2. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 3. the fan of blues is not the person who likes amber##6
 4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of jazz and the person who likes pink##2
 6. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person who likes amber##5
 7. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 9. the person who likes green is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of metal##7
10. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
11. the person who likes pink is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes pink is not the fan of ambient##6
13. the person who likes coral is somewhere between the person who likes white and the person who likes pink##7
14. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
15. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
16. the person who likes pink is not the fan of jazz##6
17. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
18. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
19. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5

