The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, handball, skiing, snowboarding, swimming, tennis
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, blues, d&b, funk, reggae, jazz, indie
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the fan of funk##7
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 3. the fan of indie is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 8. the fan of jazz is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the fan of reggae##5
10. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
12. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
13. the fan of electronic is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the fan of funk##7
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of blues##1
15. the fan of indie is the person who's sport is cricket##1
16. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
17. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
18. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2    |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |     7     |
| Sport       | swimming | cricket | snowboarding | tennis | skiing     | cycling | handball  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | indie   | blues   | reggae | jazz | electronic    | funk |

