 1. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
 2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person driving the roller##7
 4. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 8. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
 9. the person driving the bike is the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person driving the roller is the person playing chess##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
12. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
13. the person playing go is on the far left##1
14. the person driving the ship is the person playing poker##1
15. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
16. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
17. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
18. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
